items.name: Pokémon Café Mix Artstyle | Clothes Lora (Pokemon cafe remix)
items.description:
我很喜欢《宝可缤纷趣》可爱又治愈的画风。尝试训练了一个。结果意外的是，学习到的衣物特征比画风要素还多XD。但即使这样使用这个Lora确实可以帮助输出扁平化的可爱画风。非常适合使用于可爱风的福瑞创作。

权重建议0.7~1.0。（建议可以使用LoRA Block Weight插件的:OUTALL进行画风分层）

一些基础触发词：happy, blush stickers, pmcafe, pokemon cafe mix, chibi, pokemon \(creature\), clothed pokemon,

宝可缤纷趣的制服触发词： red neckerchief, red apron, cabbie hat, red headwear,

I really like the cute and healing style of “Pokémon Café Mix”. I tried training a Lora model and the result was surprising. The model learned more clothing features than style elements XD. But even so, using this Lora can help output a flat, cute style. It is very suitable for use in cute style furry creations.

The recommended weight is 0.7~1.0. (It is recommended to use the LoRA Block Weight plugin’s :OUTALL for better artstyle output)

Some basic trigger prompt: happy, blush stickers, pmcafe, pokemon cafe mix, chibi, pokemon (creature), clothed pokemon,

Pokémon Café Mix uniform prompt: red neckerchief, red apron, cabbie hat, red headwear.

items.name: Mogami (Kancolle)
items.description:
An experimental character LoRA of Mogami from Kantai Collection.

Info

Training with 66 images
Followed the manual form [ [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free ],
You can access to this guide in Suggested Resources section.

Recommended set up

Sampler: Euler a, DPM family series
Sampling steps: 20 or 25+
CFG Scale: 7
CLIP Skip: 2
*Do not use [restore face] on anime character!*

LoRA Weighting: [1 - 0.8], (1 - 0.65)

Baking Step:
0. Drafting (512 x 512 res to find your desired sketch)
1. Hires fix (txt2img: 768 x 768, 768 x 512, 512 x 768, or above res)
2. inpaint (img2img: refine some unwanted effect, [Euler a] with 50+ step)
3. Upscaling (img2img: res*2 with [ControlNet Tile] & Ultimate SD upscale)

Upscaler for [Step 1 - 3]: [R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, 4x-AnimeSharp, 4x-UltraSharp]
I always skip Step 0, 2 :P

Basic prompts

MogamiKC, serafuku, (brown) sailor collar, (black) neckerchief, (brown) shorts, (black) socks, boots
MogamiKaiNiKC, (KN) serafuku, (brown) shirt, (brown) sailor collar, (orange) neckerchief, (brown) shorts, (brown) socks

Some additional tags that you may use for reference

-swept bangs
-(long sleeves) serafuku, belt, kneehighs

[Kai Ni]
-(KN) sailor collar, (orange) sailor collar, (brown) neckerchief
-(light brown) sailor collar, (light brown) sleeve cuff

-green eyes

items.name: Kiruko Takehaya
items.description:
v1.0

Haven't checked if it works with other LoRA models. Itself model trained on 768x768 resolution. Character from the anime «Heavenly Delusion». This character's name is Kiruko, but I made a tagging mistake and included the name of the former owner of this body, namely his sister Kiriko. Thus, you may even get the impression that this body contains Kiriko's sister, not her brother Haruki. The LoRA model won't be affected by this of course, the main thing is not to get one letter wrong.

Tips: scale - 1 will be good

Training model: NAI

Used to generate models: darkSushiMixMix_225D, 7th_anime_v3, CounterfeitV30_v30

Keywords: Kiriko Takehaya

Optional keywords: white jacket, black shirt, jeans (for her outfit), also u can add brown shoes (but i'm not sure that this tag works well, so use it on your decision)

All images were generated at 384x512 resolution and upscaled using Hires.fix

Upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

Hires steps: 15-25

Denoising strength: 0.6-0.75

Upscale by: 2


If u know how to improve model, let me know, also report bugs that u find, i will try to fix them.
